```css
/* 🌿 Cool‑Calm Palette */
:root {
  --accent: #4E8B80;
  --accent-hover: #67A799;
  --accent-active: #204641;
  --highlight-bg: #E0ECE9;
  --text-main: #1F2E2B;
  --bg-main: #E8F2EF;
}

/* Basic layout */
body {
  background-color: var(--bg-main);
  color: var(--text-main);
  font-family: "Open Sans", Calibri, sans-serif;
}

h1, h2 {
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.5em;
}

/* Buttons or links */
button,
a {
  color: var(--accent);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.2s ease-in-out;
}

button:hover,
a:hover {
  color: var(--accent-hover);
}

button:active,
a:active {
  color: var(--accent-active);
}

/* Highlighted section */
.highlight {
  background-color: var(--highlight-bg);
  padding: 1rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
}
```

This snippet provides gentle transitions and keeps contrast consistent across states; you can adjust spacing or radius for your brand style.  

